<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12" style="text-align:center; position: relative;">
      <img style="max-width:100%; max-height:100%;" src="http://iacs-courses.seas.harvard.edu/courses/iacs_projects/www.equityforecast.com/images/stockmarket.jpg"/><br><br>
      <!-- Trigger the modal with a button -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3" style="text-align:center; position: relative;">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">판매 신청하기</button>
          <p>
             판매 신청하고자하는 팀 : <input type="text" name="teamname" style="font-weight:bold;" value="<%#= current_user.name %>금융" readonly/><br>
             판매하고자 하는 상품 1개당 가격 : <input type="text" name="selleachprice" required/>
             판매 신청하려는 상품의 갯수 : <input type="text" name="selleach" required/>
             <button type="submit" id="input-submit" class="btn btn-secondary" style="height:7vw; font-size:3vw;"><i class="fa fa-line-chart" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;<b>판매 신청하기</b></button>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6" style="text-align:center;">
      <table class="table-info table-hover" style="text-align:center;">
           <h2>
             <strong>Buy side <br>
               <h3>현재 나온 이 팀의 상품을 사고싶다면!</h3>
             </strong>
           </h2>
        <thead class="thead-inverse">
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>이름</th>
            <th>사고싶은 물량</th>
            <th>사고싶은 개당 가격</th>
            <th>구매 신청</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">1</th>
            <td>Mark</td>
            <td>2개</td>
            <td>1000원</td>
            <td><button type="button" class="btn btn-success-outline waves-effect">구매 신청하기</button></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">2</th>
            <td>Jacob</td>
            <td>3개</td>
            <td>1500원</td>
            <td><button type="button" class="btn btn-success-outline waves-effect">구매 신청하기</button></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">3</th>
            <td>Larry</td>
            <td>5개</td>
            <td>2000원</td>
            <td><button type="button" class="btn btn-success-outline waves-effect">구매 신청하기</button></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6" style="text-align:center;">
     <h2>
       <strong>Sell side <br>
          <h3>현재 이 팀 상품을 판매하고 있는 사람들!</h3>
       </strong>
     </h2>
      <table class="table-warning table-hover" style="text-align:center;">
        <thead class="thead-inverse">
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>이름</th>
            <th>판매하고자하는 물량</th>
            <th>판매하려는 개당 가격</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">1</th>
            <td>Mark</td>
            <td>5개</td>
            <td>2000원</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">2</th>
            <td>Jacob</td>
            <td>8개</td>
            <td>3000원</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">3</th>
            <td>Larry</td>
            <td>7개</td>
            <td>1800원</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
